Package: obc
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: Oxford Oberon-2 compiler
 This compiler translates Oberon-2 into a portable bytecode, and comes
 with an interpreter (or on some architecures, a JIT) for the bytecode.
